  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine whether treatment with a PI3K inhibitor plus
      letrozole leads to an increase in pathologic clinical response and Objective Response Rate
      compared to treatment with placebo plus letrozole in patients with Breast cancer
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
